Id #
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <title>My web page</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="index.css">
        <style media="screen">
            #red{color: red}
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
<h2>Hello there </h2>
<h2 id="red">My name is nandini </h2>
<h3>Welcome back to</h3>
<h3>our channel</h3>
<p> <big> Thanks for watching our video</big></p>
    </body>
</html>
Universal  *
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <title>My web page</title>


        <link rel="stylesheet" href="index.css">
        <style media="screen">
            *{color: red}
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
           <h2>Hello there </h2>
           <h2>My name is nandini </h2>
           <h3 style="color: green">Welcome back to</h3>
           <h3>our channel</h3>
           <p> <big> Thanks for watching our video</big></p>
  </body>
















</html>
Grouping & Class Selector in CSS
html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
                <style media="screen">
                h2.red{color: red}
                </style>
        <title>My web page</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="index.css">
    </head>
    <body>
<h1 class="red">Hello </h1>
<h2  class="red">there </h2>
<h3 >my name is </h3>
<p>nandni lodha</p>
    </body>
</html>
Css
h2.red{color: red}







