<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Pseudo Classes</title>
    <style media="screen">
     h4::first-letter{
       color: red;
       font-size: 24px;
     }
     h3::first-line{
       color: red;
       font-size: 24px;
     }
     p::selection{
       background-color: black;
       color: yellow;
     }
     h4::before{
       content: "Hello everyone"
     }
     p::after{
       content: "adios amigo"
     }




     </style>
  </head>
  <body>
Hello everyone, how's everything going!!!
<p>Hello everyone, how's everything going!!!</p>
<h3>Hello everyone, how's everything going!!!</h3>
<h4> How's everything going!!!
Hello everyone, how's everything going!!!Hello everyone, how's everything going!!!Hello everyone, how's everything going!!!</h4>
